ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectOrder approving the Change Boundaries to Beaver Valley Chamber of Commerce of Thornbury and District
PrecisOrder approving the application by the BEAVER VALLEY CHAMBER OF COMMERCE OF THORNBURY AND DISTRICT, in Ontario, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from all the Township of Collingwood, and lots 1 to 21 inclusive in concessions 1 to 4 in the Township of Euphrasia to the boundaries of the municipality of the Town of the Blue Mountains.
